Title: A Journey Through Pines
Writer: Jimmy Andrews (novel), Laura De los Santos (screenplay)
Actors: Enrique Abada, Haley Babula, Elizabeth Burcham, Austin Burns
Plot: A daughter finds a journal her dad left behind, only to discover there was another woman in his life she knew nothing about. She sets out to find this woman and the reason her father never ended up with the woman he must have loved.
